    {t:'Level 3 Analysis',d:'AI-powered input threat scoring using a second Ollama model invocation. Scores 1–10; blocks inputs scoring ≥5. Increases attack surface (the scoring prompt itself is injectable) and adds latency.'},
    {t:'Mistral 7B Instruct',d:'The LLM used by the TMC chatbot. 7 billion parameters, 8K context window, instruction-tuned. Runs natively on the Mac Metal GPU via Ollama. Uses ~5.6 GB VRAM; loads fully on M5 Pro with 64 GB unified memory.'},
    {t:'Multi-Turn Injection',d:'A prompt injection technique that establishes a trusted persona (developer, admin) across multiple conversation turns before requesting sensitive information. "Consistently successful" — more effective than single-shot injection.'},
    {t:'Narrative Injection',d:'A class of prompt injection that uses creative framing (diary entry, poem, fictional interview) to bypass surface-level content restrictions. In TMC pentest: diary entry format extracted API keys and DB connection strings.'},
    {t:'Obfuscation Bypass',d:'Encoding or transforming a prompt injection payload to evade pattern-based filters. Techniques: Pig Latin (100%), Base64, Unicode escaping, token splitting, ROT13, 1337 speak.'},
    {t:'Ollama',d:'The local LLM inference server used by the TMC chatbot. Runs natively on macOS, using the Metal GPU for acceleration. Port 11434. The chatbot container connects to it via host.docker.internal:11434.'},
    {t:'RAG',d:'Retrieval-Augmented Generation. The TMC chatbot uses RAG to retrieve relevant knowledge base documents before generating a response. Attack vectors: inject malicious content into retrieved documents; query for sensitive documents (keys.md).'},
    {t:'RAG Fishing',d:'A broad technique of sending semantically similar queries to trigger retrieval of sensitive documents from a vector database, when you don\'t know exactly what\'s indexed.'},
    {t:'Rate Limiting',d:'The TMC chatbot enforces: 30 req/min on /api/chat, 5/min on /api/login, 3/min on /api/register. Empirical testing found ~150 req/min possible before throttling.'},
